SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThree mothers at the heart of a review
OL,8,Finto maternity failings at Nottingham
OL,9,Fhospitals have told of their
OL,10,Fdevastation at the harms they've
OL,11,Fendured.
OL,13,FJenny, Sarah, and Mel have shared
OL,14,Ftheir stories of miscarriages, being
OL,15,Fleft without proper treatment, and
OL,16,Ftrauma which will 'never ever leave'.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThe inquiry, led by senior midwife
OL,8,FDonna Ockenden and published on
OL,9,FWednesday, has been driven by families
OL,10,Fseeking answers as to why their
OL,11,Fhealthy babies died during labour or
OL,12,Fshortly after birth, or were left with
OL,13,Fdisabilities.
OL,15,FIn a statement, the Trust has
OL,16,Fapologised unreservedly and says it
OL,17,Ffully accepts the findings of the
OL,18,Freview. It says it will now take time
OL,19,Fto carefully consider and reflect
OL,20,Ffurther on its recommendations.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThe biggest maternity review in NHS
OL,8,Fhistory has exposed 162 deaths -
OL,9,Fincluding 156 children and six mothers
OL,10,F- could have been avoided if they were
OL,11,Fgiven better care.
OL,13,FIt's been driven by families seeking
OL,14,Fanswers as to why their healthy babies
OL,15,Fdied during labour or shortly after
OL,16,Fbirth, or were left with disabilities.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThe Ockendon report, an independent
OL,8,Finquiry into maternity services in
OL,9,FNottingham, has included the cases of
OL,10,F2,500 families over a 20-year period,
OL,11,Fand serious and deadly incidents in
OL,12,Fmaternity care and found a string of
OL,13,F"repeated failures".
OL,15,FJenny Ardley-Oakden was a teacher in
OL,16,FNottingham who fractured her coccyx
OL,17,Fduring her first labour.
OL,19,FShe was diagnosed with pelvic girdle
OL,20,Fpain in her second pregnancy and ended
OL,21,Fup having an emergency caesarean.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FMs Ardley-Oakden said: "They kept
OL,8,Fgiving me multiple scans and there was
OL,9,Fa debate about what size Daniel was
OL,10,Fgoing to be.
OL,12,F"In the end he was eight pounds eight,
OL,13,Fbut I'm five foot one. There was only
OL,14,Fa very brief conversation about
OL,15,Fpossibly having a C-section. Having
OL,16,Flooked at my notes I think there was a
OL,17,Fcomplete lack of risk assessment."
OL,19,FAfter her son Daniel was born, Jenny
OL,20,Fneeded further surgery - and ended up
OL,21,Fhaving 10 operations across 12 years.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FIn one operation she told ITV News
OL,8,FCentral she had lost more than 10
OL,9,Fpints of blood.
OL,11,FShe said: "I got to hold my baby for
OL,12,Fjust a couple of seconds, and I was
OL,13,Fjust really aware that things weren't
OL,14,Fhappening as they should. It just
OL,15,Fdidn't feel right. In the end I had
OL,16,Falmost four hours almost fully
OL,17,Fconscious surgery. I lost 16 pints of
OL,18,Fblood.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"At what turned out to be near the end
OL,8,Fof the surgery, I realised I could
OL,9,Fstart to feel it, so I managed to move
OL,10,Fone finger to try and get their
OL,11,Fattention, and then they realised that
OL,12,FI could feel it.
OL,14,F"They gave me a choice which seemed
OL,15,Fvery odd, and they offered me did I
OL,16,Fwant a general anaesthetic and I
OL,17,Fdidn't know what to do.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"An hour earlier I'd nearly died. I
OL,8,Fwas just terrified. I hadn't held my
OL,9,Fbaby properly. So in the end I said
OL,10,Fkeep going, because I thought if I had
OL,11,Fa general anaesthetic, I thought I
OL,12,Fwould die.
OL,14,F"So I had about 15 minutes where they
OL,15,Fwere stitching me up that wasn't
OL,16,Fanaesthetised properly and I still
OL,17,Fhave flashbacks now of the cuts and
OL,18,Fthe pulling and that physical
OL,19,Fsensation will never, ever leave me.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"I've had ten operations in 12 years.
OL,8,FI'm now officially registered
OL,9,Fdisabled. I can't teach full time, a
OL,10,Fjob I absolutely love, because of my
OL,11,Fcognitive processing, and my memory,
OL,12,Fand some of my speech has been
OL,13,Fseverely effected by PTSD.
OL,15,F"I consider that I was able-bodied
OL,16,Fwhen I went into QMC (Queen's Medical
OL,17,FCentre) on 28 April to have my baby
OL,18,Fboy, and I came out mentally and
OL,19,Fphysically disabled."
OL,26,@xD@VpmyD@Gpn
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FDespite receiving consultant care
OL,8,Fwhile pregnant with her son, Sarah
OL,9,FMcCrackle believes delays in hospital
OL,10,Fadmission led to his death.
OL,12,FShe said: "I'd rang the hospital 17
OL,13,Ftimes, repeating 'I need to come in, I
OL,14,Fknow I'm in labour.' They kept telling
OL,15,Fme I wasn't in labour, and you just
OL,16,Fbelieve it at the time, you just think
OL,17,F'well they know best.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FSarah was told to stay at home because
OL,8,Fthere were no beds available. After 17
OL,9,Fhours she headed into the hospital
OL,10,Fwhere staff took her to an empty
OL,11,Fantenatal ward.
OL,13,FShe continued: "They left us there for
OL,14,Ffour hours, and after that they took
OL,15,Fus into a small room, and then all of
OL,16,Fa sudden there were nine doctors,
OL,17,Fthree midwives, and the scan lady. She
OL,18,Fliterally put the scan machine across
OL,19,Fonce, back again, and she said
OL,20,F'there's no heartbeat.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"My partner ran into the corner of the
OL,8,Froom screaming. I'd never heard her
OL,9,Fscream like that.
OL,11,FAs part of the review's findings,
OL,12,FSarah was also told that failings were
OL,13,Ffound in another of her pregnancies.
OL,15,F"(My baby) was 17 weeks old and I
OL,16,Fpresented for a stitch to my cervix to
OL,17,Fhold it in place. I have no idea how
OL,18,Fit happened, but they placed a pessary
OL,19,Finside me, which caused a medical
OL,20,Fabortion. She was perfectly beautiful.
OL,21,FShe just looked asleep. Tiny doll.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"I'm not the mother I was. I'm not the
OL,8,FSarah I was. I've seen the impact it
OL,9,Fhad on me and my family, and this,
OL,10,Fwhat I'm doing, is predominantly for
OL,11,Fthem, so we can get answers,
OL,12,Faccountability."
OL,14,FSarah remembers comments made by
OL,15,Fmaternity staff after each of her 14
OL,16,Fmiscarriages, including:
OL,18,F"You've lost again, never mind."
OL,20,F"What is this your 50th miscarriage?"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"She knows where everything is, she's
OL,8,Fa regular."
OL,10,FAt almost 24 weeks pregnant, Mel
OL,11,FIbrahim went to hospital after
OL,12,Fexperiencing bleeding and painful
OL,13,Fcontractions. She spent two days in
OL,14,Fthe labour suite and was then
OL,15,Funexpectedly moved.
OL,17,FHer daughter Amaya spent her first
OL,18,Feight months of life in hospital. She
OL,19,Flived with a brain injury, cerebral
OL,20,Fpalsy and is profoundly deaf and
OL,21,Fnonverbal.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FShe said: "So many people did save her
OL,8,Flife, and for that we'll be forever
OL,9,Fgrateful. We've got our little girl,
OL,10,Fbut we're in the review for a reason.
OL,12,F"I was at high risk, it was on my
OL,13,Fnotes that I was at high risk, but
OL,14,Fthey still put me in a room on the
OL,15,Fantenatal clinic, I was all on my own.
OL,16,FI was right at the end of the corridor
OL,17,Faway from anyone, and there was no
OL,18,Fmedical equipment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"The midwife, she showed me around the
OL,8,Fsmall room, she showed me where there
OL,9,Fwas an emergency buzzer that not
OL,10,Feveryone gets shown, and I forever
OL,11,Fwill be grateful that she actually
OL,12,Ftold me about that, because the
OL,13,Ffollowing day, in the middle of the
OL,14,Fnight I called for a midwife, I had
OL,15,Fcontraction like pains again.
OL,17,F"She gave me paracetamol, did a blood
OL,18,Fpressure check on me and just said
OL,19,F'let's see how it goes.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"About three or four hours later, I
OL,8,Fgot up and went to the bathroom, and I
OL,9,Fsaw what I thought was a blood clot,
OL,10,Fand then I realised it was Amaya's
OL,11,Fhead.
OL,13,F"I have no idea quite how I did it but
OL,14,FI caught her. She was the size of my
OL,15,Fhand, she looked like a bird.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"I didn't know what to do, the
OL,8,Fmidwives didn't know what to do. No
OL,9,Fone knew what to do because this was
OL,10,Fthe antenatal clinic. There was no
OL,11,Fequipment and no one who was skilled
OL,12,Fin managing an extremely pre-term
OL,13,Fbirth.
OL,15,F"I knew that she was resuscitated, but
OL,16,FI didn't know until I went through her
OL,17,Frecords that it took 20 minutes, and
OL,18,Ffive attempts to intubate her, because
OL,19,Fthere wasn't anyone with the skills to
OL,20,Fbe able to do that.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G18/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"So that little girl went almost 20
OL,8,Fminutes without actually having oxygen
OL,9,Fsupport.
OL,11,F"I don't always want to focus on the
OL,12,Fnegatives about Amaya. Amaya is an
OL,13,Famazing girl. She is this cheeky,
OL,14,Fsassy girl. She's a bright star."
OL,16,F"We failed you": the bosses of
OL,17,FNottingham University Hospitals Trust
OL,18,Frespond
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G19/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FIn a statement responding to the
OL,8,Freview, the Nottingham University
OL,9,FHospital NHS Trust said, "Today,
OL,10,FWednesday 24 June, the findings from
OL,11,Fthe Independent Maternity Review (IMR)
OL,12,Finto services at Nottingham University
OL,13,FHospitals NHS Trust (NUH) were
OL,14,Fpublished.
OL,16,F"The Review, led by Donna Ockenden,
OL,17,Foutlines how, where and why care in
OL,18,Four services had resulted in harm to
OL,19,Fmothers and babies in their hospitals
OL,20,Fand made recommendations of actions to
OL,21,Fimprove care in the future.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G20/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
