OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"Wefullyaccept thefindings of the
OL,8,FReview andtake responsibility for the
OL,9,Ffailings that are detailed within it.
OL,10,FAn initial response to the review,
OL,11,Fshared by Chief Executive Anthony May
OL,12,Fand Trust Chair Nick Carver, follows.
OL,14,F"We will now take time to carefully
OL,15,Fconsider and reflect further on the
OL,16,FReview outcomes and its
OL,17,Frecommendations."
OL,19,FThey've also written an open letter to
OL,20,Fthe people of Nottinghamshire:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G21/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34222
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"The publication of the independent
OL,8,Freview into maternity services in
OL,9,FNottingham is a watershed moment for
OL,10,Faffected families, our staff and for
OL,11,Fthe communities we serve.
OL,13,F"We apologise unreservedly to the
OL,14,Fwomen and families who have suffered
OL,15,Fharm, loss, trauma or distress while
OL,16,Freceiving care in our services. We
OL,17,Ffailed you, and on behalf of
OL,18,FNottingham University Hospitals Trust,
OL,19,Fwe accept responsibility for our
OL,20,Ffailings.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G22/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34223
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"Many families have been generous
OL,8,Fenough to meet with us, showing
OL,9,Fextraordinary courage and
OL,10,Fdetermination. We are grateful for
OL,11,Fthat, and we want you to know that the
OL,12,Fpublication of this report is not the
OL,13,Fend of a process. It is another
OL,14,Fimportant milestone in a journey that
OL,15,Fmust continue. Your bravery and
OL,16,Fcommitment to speaking up is helping
OL,17,Fimprove maternity care.
OL,19,F"We want to thank Donna Ockenden for
OL,20,Fher work and for engaging with us
OL,21,Fthroughout this process."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G23/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34224
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThe NHS Trust added, "We recognise
OL,8,Fthat trust is earned through actions,
OL,9,Fnot words. We know, also, that
OL,10,Ffamilies and the wider public will
OL,11,Fjudge us not by what we say today, but
OL,12,Fby what we do next.
OL,14,F"The review makes clear that while
OL,15,Fimprovements have been made, there is
OL,16,Fstill more to do. We will take time to
OL,17,Freflect on the report with humility,
OL,18,Fhonesty and determination.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G24/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34225
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"At the same time, we will work with
OL,8,Ffamilies on a meaningful apology
OL,9,Fbecause we know it is important to
OL,10,Fthem that this is reflective of the
OL,11,Ffindings of the review, and our
OL,12,Fcommitment to lasting improvement. We
OL,13,Fcan say with certainty that families
OL,14,Fwill continue to be involved in our
OL,15,Fimprovement plans because this review
OL,16,Fhas proved that we can learn from them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G25/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34226
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782362901
OL,3,CBaby loss, trauma and disability:
OL,4,CLives changed by Nottingham maternity
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"We must also acknowledge our staff.
OL,8,FEvery day we see dedicated,
OL,9,Fcompassionate professionals working
OL,10,Ftirelessly to provide the best
OL,11,Fpossible care for women and families,
OL,12,Foften under extreme pressure and
OL,13,Fscrutiny."
OL,15,FThe statement concluded, "On behalf of
OL,16,Fthe Trust, we renew the commitments to
OL,17,Ftransparency, openness and
OL,18,Faccountability. Most importantly, we
OL,19,Frenew our commitment to providing
OL,20,Fsafe, high-quality maternity care at
OL,21,Fyour hospitals."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G26/27
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
